                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM03001 CO-UBM03001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3400-KABCC26-SELECT-EXT.
           EXIT.
