      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  한신평재무업종구분별 재무재표정보조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3420-KABCC26-SELECT-RTN.

           EVALUATE  WK-H-O-F-BZTYP-DSTCD
      *#1 은행인경우
           WHEN 'AA'
      *@2     은행 제무재표조회
               PERFORM  S3421-KABCC26-BANK-SEL-RTN
                  THRU  S3421-KABCC26-BANK-SEL-EXT
      *#2 금융기관일경우
           WHEN 'BB'
           WHEN 'CC'
           WHEN 'DD'
           WHEN 'EE'
           WHEN 'FF'
           WHEN 'GG'
           WHEN 'HH'
           WHEN 'II'
           WHEN 'JJ'
           WHEN 'KK'
           WHEN 'ZZ'
      *@3     금융기관 제무재표조회
