                AND  한신평업체코드     = :WK-H-O-ENTP-CD
                AND  한신평결산자료구분 = 'K'
                AND  한신평보고서구분   = '19'
                AND  결산년월일     IN (:WK-STLACC-YMD,
                                        :WK-STLACC-YMD-1,
                                        :WK-STLACC-YMD-2)
               WITH  UR
           END-EXEC

      *   리턴코드가 정상이 아니면 에러처리
           EVALUATE  SQLCODE
               WHEN  CO-OK
                     CONTINUE
               WHEN  CO-NOT-FOUND
      *              금융총비용비율(금융비용/총비용비율)
                     MOVE  0           TO  WK-FNCS-RATO
                                           WK-FNCS-RATO-1
                                           WK-FNCS-RATO-2
      *              매출채권회전비율
                     MOVE  0           TO  WK-ASALE-RATO
                                           WK-ASALE-RATO-1
                                           WK-ASALE-RATO-2

               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KABCC23'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'SELECT'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'GIUP-DATA-02 시오류가발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM03001 CO-UBM03001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
            END-EVALUATE

           .
       S3424-KABCC23-GIUP-SEL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   DATA MOVE
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3400-DATA-MOVE-RTN.

      *   초기화
           INITIALIZE    OT-REC

      *@1 출력데이터조립:한신평업체코드,법인등록번호,
      *@한신평산업코드,결산년월일,영업신용등급구분,
      *@평가년월일,유효년월일,법인세차감전게속사업이익(전전년),
      *@법인세차감전게속사업이익(전년),자기자본(기준년),
      *@영업이익,이자수익,감가상각비,금융비용,
      *@단기차입금(기준년),업체총차입금,자산총계,매출액
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *   공통자료
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *   한신평업체코드 = THKABCB01_한신평업체코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-ENTP-CD        TO  OT-ENTP-CD

      *   고객식별자   = THKABCB01_고객식별자(대체번호)
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CUST-IDNFR     TO  OT-CUST-IDNFR

      *   한신평산업코드(표준산업분류코드)
      *          = THKABCB01_한신평산업코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-IDSTRY-CD      TO  OT-IDSTRY-CD

      *   한신평재무업종구분 = THKABCB01_한신평업체코드
180416*   한신평재무업종구분 SPACE방지를 위해 제조로 변경
           IF  WK-H-O-F-BZTYP-DSTCD = SPACE
               MOVE  CO-CHA-00
                 TO  OT-F-BZTYP-DSTCD
           ELSE
               MOVE  WK-H-O-F-BZTYP-DSTCD
                 TO  OT-F-BZTYP-DSTCD
           END-IF

      *   결산년월일  = THKABCC26_MAX(결산년월일)
           MOVE  WK-STLACC-YMD         TO  OT-STLACC-YMD

      *   영업신용등급구분  = THKIIK616_영업신용등급구분
           MOVE  WK-H-O-LAST-CRTDSCD   TO  OT-LAST-CRTDSCD

      *   평가년월일        = THKIIK616_평가년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-VALUA-YMD      TO  OT-VALUA-YMD

      *   유효년월일        = THKIIK616_유효년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-VALD-YMD       TO  OT-VALD-YMD
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *   금융기관(은행)
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *   법인세차감전게속사업이익(전전년)
           MOVE  WK-BBC-AMT-2          TO  OT-BBC-AMT-2

      *   법인세차감전게속사업이익(전년)
           MOVE  WK-BBC-AMT-1          TO  OT-BBC-AMT-1

      *   법인세차감전게속사업이익(기준년)
           MOVE  WK-BBC-AMT            TO  OT-BBC-AMT

      *   자기자본(전전년)
           MOVE  WK-JGJ-AMT-2          TO  OT-JGJ-AMT-2

      *   자기자본(전년)
           MOVE  WK-JGJ-AMT-1          TO  OT-JGJ-AMT-1

      *   자기자본(기준년)
           MOVE  WK-JGJ-AMT            TO  OT-JGJ-AMT
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *   금융기관 외 기업
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *    1.영업이익
170706     MOVE WK-YUI-AMT-2           TO  OT-YUI-AMT-2
170706     MOVE WK-YUI-AMT-1           TO  OT-YUI-AMT-1
           MOVE WK-YUI-AMT             TO  OT-YUI-AMT

      *    2.이자수익
           MOVE  WK-IJS-AMT-2          TO  OT-IJS-AMT-2
           MOVE  WK-IJS-AMT-1          TO  OT-IJS-AMT-1
           MOVE  WK-IJS-AMT            TO  OT-IJS-AMT

      *    3.감가상각비
           MOVE  WK-GGS-AMT-2          TO  OT-GGS-AMT-2
           MOVE  WK-GGS-AMT-1          TO  OT-GGS-AMT-1
           MOVE  WK-GGS-AMT            TO  OT-GGS-AMT

      *    8.금융비용
           MOVE  WK-GYB-AMT-2          TO  OT-GYB-AMT-2
           MOVE  WK-GYB-AMT-1          TO  OT-GYB-AMT-1
           MOVE  WK-GYB-AMT            TO  OT-GYB-AMT

      *    10.단기차입금(기준년)
           MOVE  WK-DGC-AMT-2          TO  OT-DGC-AMT-2
           MOVE  WK-DGC-AMT-1          TO  OT-DGC-AMT-1
           MOVE  WK-DGC-AMT            TO  OT-DGC-AMT

      *    20.업체총차입금
           MOVE  WK-YCC-AMT-2          TO  OT-YCC-AMT-2
           MOVE  WK-YCC-AMT-1          TO  OT-YCC-AMT-1
           MOVE  WK-YCC-AMT            TO  OT-YCC-AMT

      *    21.자산총계
           MOVE  WK-JSC-AMT-2          TO  OT-JSC-AMT-2
           MOVE  WK-JSC-AMT-1          TO  OT-JSC-AMT-1
           MOVE  WK-JSC-AMT            TO  OT-JSC-AMT

      *    22.매출액
           MOVE  WK-MCA-AMT-2          TO  OT-MCA-AMT-2
           MOVE  WK-MCA-AMT-1          TO  OT-MCA-AMT-1
           MOVE  WK-MCA-AMT            TO  OT-MCA-AMT

211022*    금융총비용비율(금융비용/총비용비율)
           MOVE  WK-FNCS-RATO-2        TO  OT-FNCS-RATO-2
           MOVE  WK-FNCS-RATO-1        TO  OT-FNCS-RATO-1
           MOVE  WK-FNCS-RATO          TO  OT-FNCS-RATO

      *    매출채권회전비율
           MOVE  WK-ASALE-RATO-2       TO  OT-ASALE-RATO-2
           MOVE  WK-ASALE-RATO-1       TO  OT-ASALE-RATO-1
           MOVE  WK-ASALE-RATO         TO  OT-ASALE-RATO

      *    현금성자산금액(현금및현금성자산)
           MOVE  WK-CSH-AMT-2          TO  OT-CSH-AMT-2
           MOVE  WK-CSH-AMT-1          TO  OT-CSH-AMT-1
           MOVE  WK-CSH-AMT            TO  OT-CSH-AMT

           .
       S3400-DATA-MOVE-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   DATA WRITE
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3500-DATA-WRITE-RTN.

      *@1  DATA WRITE
           WRITE OT-REC

      *   리턴코드가 정상이 아니면 에러처리
           IF  WK-OT-FILE-ST NOT = CO-STAT-OK
               MOVE 'OT-FILE WRITE ERROR : FILE-ST IS '
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               MOVE  WK-OT-FILE-ST     TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG(34:2)
               #ERROR  CO-EBM02001 CO-UBM02001 CO-STAT-ERROR
               #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-IF

           ADD   CO-NUM-1              TO  WK-AC-WRITE-CNT
